-- Sony, Samsung Optical-Disc Price-Fixing Suit Can Proceed Amid U.S. Probe
-- Edvard Pettersson
-- 2010-06-24T21:45:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/sony-samsung-optical-disc-price-fixing-suit-can-proceed-amid-u-s-probe.html

          
          
             A civil lawsuit accusing Sony Corp.,
Samsung Electronics Co. and other makers of optical disc drives
used in CD, DVD and Blu-ray players of price-fixing can proceed
while the U.S. government pursues a criminal investigation.  
